code: import Cookies from"js-cookie";export const setSessionCookie=session=>{Cookies.remove("session");Cookies.set("session",session,{expires:14});};export const getSessionCookie=()=>{const sessionCookie=Cookies.get("session");if(sessionCookie===undefined){return{};}else{return JSON.parse(sessionCookie);}};export const dropCookie=()=>{Cookies.remove("session");return;};
